 one\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the hard battle, the amazing opponents, everybody was healthy and came to fight.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hard battle\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"the amazing opponents\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am the wolf among wolves.\\\"\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wolf\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"wolves\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles is the closest thing athletics has right now to a global superstar.\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2463, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2395}, {\"ngram\": \"the closest thing athletics\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"a global superstar\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was placed front and centre of the Netflix documentarySprint, which aimed to sprinkle a little of theDrive to Survivemagic in athletics' direction.\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2502, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.041851772781525e-12, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"centre\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"theDrive\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"Survivemagic\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2589}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics' direction\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a sport always fighting for attention, for a more permanent place in the entertainment-scape.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2714, \"entities